(188, 2741, 'home_about_us_text', '[:en]<strong>CONSULSTAFF was founded in 1997</strong> in Italy.\r\n\r\nA qualified team in the field of international development, mergers and acquisitions of strategic planning, marketing, management accounting, accounting and tax accounting.\r\n\r\nCurrently, a team of company professionals successfully advises clients in <strong>Russia</strong>, <strong>Eastern Europe</strong> and <strong>Italy</strong>, offering them a full package of services to enter international markets, in particular the Russian and Italian markets, the formation and development of sales, accounting and tax accounting, and provides support in other specific areas of activity depending on customer needs.\r\n\r\n<strong>CONSULSTAFF</strong> is an example of the synergy of <strong>Italian traditions</strong> and <strong>quality</strong>, <strong>with the experience</strong> and <strong>dynamism of international partners</strong>. We are creating the future here and now, helping companies reach a new level.[:it]<strong>CONSULSTAFF, dal 1997</strong>, è un team di consulenti di internazionalizzazione, soprattutto verso aree <strong>russofone, M&A e amministrazione</strong>.\r\n\r\nHanno collaborato con multinazionali di consulenza strategica e molteplici imprese italiane\r\n\r\n<strong>CONSULSTAFF</strong> è sinergia tra tradizione italiana e dinamismo internazionale\r\nCreiamo futuro oggi[:ru]Компания <strong>CONSULSTAFF основана в 1997</strong> году в Италии.\r\n\r\n<strong>CONSULSTAFF</strong> – пример синергии <strong>итальянских традиций</strong> и <strong>качества</strong>, <strong>с опытом</strong> и <strong>динамизмом международных партнеров</strong>. Будущее мы создаем здесь и сейчас, помогая компаниям выйти на новый уровень.[:]'),
