(3397, 1, '2020-01-20 16:17:46', '2020-01-20 13:17:46', '[:en]In modern conditions, for many business owners and managers, issues of reducing financial risks in Russia and the effective operation of accumulated capital abroad are becoming important.\r\n\r\nSuch tasks are effectively achieved through the proper organization of international financial flow and their subsequent management and control.\r\n\r\nMany Russian companies experience difficulties and limitations in raising funds in Russia due to high lending rates and very difficult approval processes.\r\n\r\nThis forces companies to seek investment in the west. A simple appeal to Western credit institutions is ineffective and for many poorly understood process.Asset reorganization (corporatization or restructuring)\r\nFinancial recovery\r\nIncreasing the value of assets and its attractiveness to the investor\r\nSubsequent company value managementThe logical continuation of this work is the search for a specific investor or buyer.The logical continuation of this work is the search for a specific investor or buyer.When evaluating a business and managing a company\'s value, it is important to consider various aspects of extracting a company\'s value, such as financial, strategic, and organizational. To manage the value of the company, you must:When evaluating a business and managing a company\'s value, it is important to consider various aspects of extracting a company\'s value, such as financial, strategic, and organizational. To manage the value of the company, you must:create settings and cost indicators,\r\nprovide business portfolio management,\r\ncreate an organizational structure\r\nidentify value creation factors,\r\nto ensure the management of the effectiveness of the functioning of the business; and to ensure the management of the effectiveness of the work of personnel.create settings and cost indicators,\r\nprovide business portfolio management,\r\ncreate an organizational structure\r\nidentify value creation factors,\r\nto ensure the management of the effectiveness of the functioning of the business; and to ensure the management of the effectiveness of the work of personnel.When organizing a new direction in business or increasing the efficiency of an existing system, it is necessary to choose the optimal taxation system, organizational form, etc. With the help of tax planning, such a taxation system is organized that will achieve the maximum financial result at the lowest cost.[:]', '[:en]Business Planning and Investing[:it]Pianificazione aziendale e finanziamenti[:ru]Бизнес планирование и инвестирование[:]', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'investing', '', '', '2020-02-24 20:25:36', '2020-02-24 17:25:36', '', 2743, 'https://consulstaff.com/?page_id=3397', 0, 'page', '', 0),
